### 2. Missing Security Headers (OWASP A05 – Security Misconfiguration)

**Problem:** Express sends `X-Powered-By: Express` by default, advertising your stack. No `Content-Security-Policy`, `X-Frame-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, or other defensive headers are set.

**Fix:** Add [`helmet`](https://helmetjs.github.io/):

```js
