### 🟠 High

#### 4. No Rate Limiting — Denial of Service / Brute Force (OWASP A04 / A07)

There is no rate limiting on any endpoint. An attacker can flood the server with requests, cause resource exhaustion, or (on future auth endpoints) brute-force credentials.

**Fix:**

